{"tid":1395227,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真討論］香港人點樣透過工會呢樣野行使自己嘅合法權益？","createTime":"2019-08-01T16:28:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T17:33:58.000Z","uid":265248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"96621fba84b1d8be95279c72faf0bd4aadc6870b","tid":1395227,"uid":265248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T16:28:38.000Z","msg":"其實而家立法會裡面有三席係黎自勞工界，兩席係工聯會，一席係勞聯，三席都係自動當選。2017年，可以選呢三席嘅，有<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">671個</span></strong></span>已登記為選民嘅團體。<br />\n<br />\n咁我就去search下而家香港有咩工會，有啲聽過，但絕大部份你睇到真係得啖笑。詳見以下連結：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/news/TU16_add_list_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.labour.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fnews%2FTU16_add_list_c.pdf&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFOyReoVNKXL6ewaNyEagWdY%3D&h=01c85692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.labour.gov.hk/tc/news/TU16_add_list_c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n根據勞工處職工會登記局，2017年香港有<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">888個</span></strong></span>已登記職工會，申報會員人數共有91.6萬。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.labour.gov.hk/text_alternative/pdf/tc/ASR2017.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.labour.gov.hk%2Ftext_alternative%2Fpdf%2Ftc%2FASR2017.pdf&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFOyReoVNKXL6ewaNyEagWdY%3D&h=78c0c6e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.labour.gov.hk/text_alternative/pdf/tc/ASR2017.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n香港勞動人口接近400萬，居然有接近1/4嘅人口係工會會員？<br />\n<br />\n根據基本法第27條，香港居民有組織及參加工會嘅自由同埋權利，但我地有無認認真真咁行使過呢項權利？<br />\n<br />\n如果本身你所屬嘅職業已經有工會，你有無參加？<br />\n<br />\n如果無，點解唔成立一個，溝淡一下建制嘅勢力，甚至將三席建制議員踢出立法會，<br />\n<br />\n再進一步諗，我地有無可能透過組織工會，凝聚社會意見，係重要議題上面向政府施壓，甚至乎形成跨行業嘅人民議會，爭取立會及選舉委員會嘅雙普選？"},{"pid":"40decf64ad72ea90ac593f88edc3c8671bd20702","tid":1395227,"uid":265248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96621fba84b1d8be95279c72faf0bd4aadc6870b","tid":1395227,"uid":265248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"rep